#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:2
msgid "Using portable mode"
msgstr "使用可移植模式"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:4
msgid ""
"This page describes a mode some newer AppImages (i.e., built in 2017 or "
"later) provide, the *portable mode*. This mode allows for bundling an "
"application's data next to the application's AppImage."
msgstr ""
"本頁說明部分較新的 AppImage（例如 2017 年或之後建置）提供的一種模式：*可移植"
"模式*。此模式可讓應用程式資料與其 AppImage 放在一起。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:10
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "目次"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:13
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "簡介"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:15
msgid ""
"Sometimes it can be useful for data of an application to travel along with "
"the application, for example to put the application on a USB stick that can "
"be used with different computers. In the windows world, this concept is "
"known as “portable applications”."
msgstr ""
"有時讓應用程式的資料跟著應用程式一起移動會很有用，例如把應用程式放在 USB 隨身"
"碟，以便在不同電腦上使用。在 Windows 世界中，這個概念稱為「可攜式應用程式」。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:17
msgid ""
"Normally the application contained inside an AppImage will store its "
"configuration files wherever it always stores them (most frequently "
"somewhere inside :code:`$HOME`). In other words, the fact that an "
"application is contained inside an AppImage normally does not change where "
"the application stores its data."
msgstr ""
"通常 AppImage 內的應用程式會把設定檔儲存在其一貫的位置（最常見是在 :code:"
"`$HOME` 內的某處）。換句話說，應用程式被包在 AppImage 裡通常不會改變它儲存資"
"料的位置。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:19
msgid ""
"However, there is functionality in newer AppImages that can make the "
"application's data travel along with the application, if certain directories "
"are present *next to the AppImage file*."
msgstr ""
"不過，較新的 AppImage 提供一些功能，只要在 *AppImage 檔案旁* 存在特定目錄，就"
"能讓應用程式資料與應用程式一同移動。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:21
msgid ""
"If you invoke an AppImage built with a recent version of AppImageKit and "
"have one of these special directories in place, then the configuration files "
"will be stored alongside the AppImage. This can be useful for portable use "
"cases, e.g., carrying an AppImage on a USB stick, along with its data."
msgstr ""
"如果您執行的是使用新版 AppImageKit 建置的 AppImage，且已放置這些特殊目錄，設"
"定檔就會儲存在 AppImage 旁邊。這對可移植的使用情境很有用，例如把 AppImage 與"
"其資料一起放在 USB 隨身碟上。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:23
msgid ""
"If there is a directory with the same name as the AppImage plus :code:`."
"home`, then :code:`$HOME` will automatically be set to it before executing "
"the payload application"
msgstr ""
"如果有一個目錄名稱等於 AppImage 加上 :code:`.home`，則在執行實際應用程式前，:"
"code:`$HOME` 會自動設為該目錄。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:24
msgid ""
"If there is a directory with the same name as the AppImage plus :code:`."
"config`, then :code:`$XDG_CONFIG_HOME` will automatically be set to it "
"before executing the payload application"
msgstr ""
"如果有一個目錄名稱等於 AppImage 加上 :code:`.config`，則在執行實際應用程式"
"前，:code:`$XDG_CONFIG_HOME` 會自動設為該目錄。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:28
msgid "Example"
msgstr "範例"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:30
msgid ""
"Imagine you want to use the Leafpad text editor, but carry its settings "
"around with the executable. You can do the following:"
msgstr ""
"假設您想使用 Leafpad 文字編輯器，但希望設定能隨可執行檔一起攜帶。您可以這麼"
"做："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/portable-mode.rst:34
msgid ""
"# Download Leafpad AppImage and make it executable\n"
"$ wget -c \"https://bintray.com/probono/AppImages/download_file?"
"file_path=Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\" -O Leafpad-0.8.18.1."
"glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"$ chmod a+x Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"\n"
"# Create a directory with the same name as the AppImage plus the \".config\" "
"extension\n"
"# in the same directory as the AppImage\n"
"$ mkdir Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage.config\n"
"\n"
"# Run Leafpad, change some setting (e.g., change the default font size) then "
"close Leafpad\n"
"$ ./Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"\n"
"# Now, check where the settings were written:\n"
"$ find Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage.config\n"
"(...)\n"
"Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage.config/leafpad/leafpadrc"
msgstr ""
"# 下載 Leafpad AppImage 並設為可執行\n"
"$ wget -c \"https://bintray.com/probono/AppImages/download_file?"
"file_path=Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\" -O Leafpad-0.8.18.1."
"glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"$ chmod a+x Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"\n"
"# 在與 AppImage 相同的目錄中，建立與 AppImage 同名並加上 \".config\" 副檔名的"
"目錄\n"
"$ mkdir Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage.config\n"
"\n"
"# 執行 Leafpad，變更一些設定（例如變更預設字型大小）後關閉 Leafpad\n"
"$ ./Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"\n"
"# 接著檢查設定寫入的位置：\n"
"$ find Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage.config\n"
"(...)\n"
"Leafpad-0.8.18.1.glibc2.4-x86_64.AppImage.config/leafpad/leafpadrc"

